yrup, salt, caramel color, garlic powder, sugar, spices(celery seed), tamarind, natural flavor, sulphite), silicon dioxide), canola oil, citric acid, herbs, sodium diacetate, silicon dioxide (anti-caking agent), natural flavor) (sulphites).
